@erc_no
title: We don't want to partake in jxsi

Are we completely sure of this? At the moment, there is heavy expectations both within the party and from the civil society for a full commitment to National liberation.

- @erc_rethink: Wait, let's re-think this
- @erc_no_for_sure: There's no need for us to go hand-in-hand with [? if cdc_parlament_s > 0: CDC?][? if dl_parlament_s > 0: DL?][? if pdcat_parlament_s > 0: the PDeCAT?]

@erc_rethink
go-to: erc_0

@erc_no_for_sure
on-arrival: {!
    Q.erc_left_dissent += 5;
    Q.erc_core_dissent += 15;
    Q.erc_pragmatic_dissent += 10;
    Q.erc_civic_dissent += 25;

    Q.elisenda_paluzie_advisor_available = 0;
    Q.independence_trust -= 15;

    const _activeCiu = Q.cdc_parlament_s > 0 ? "cdc" : Q.dl_parlament_s > 0 ? "dl" : "pdcat";
    for (const c of Q.parlament_constituencies) {
        Q["erc_parlament_" + c + "_buss_support"] -= 5;
        Q["abstain_parlament_" + c + "_buss_support"] += 1.5;
        Q["cup_parlament_" + c + "_buss_support"] += 1.5;
        Q[_activeCiu + "_parlament_" + c + "_buss_support"] += 3;
        Q["erc_parlament_" + c + "_ind_support"] -= 1;
        Q["cup_parlament_" + c + "_ind_support"] += 0.5;
        Q["abstain_parlament_" + c + "_ind_support"] += 0.5;
        Q["erc_parlament_" + c + "_young_support"] -= 7.5;
        Q["abstain_parlament_" + c + "_young_support"] += 2.5;
        Q["cup_parlament_" + c + "_young_support"] += 3;
        Q[_activeCiu + "_parlament_" + c + "_young_support"] += 2;
        Q["erc_parlament_" + c + "_rural_support"] -= 15;
        if(Q["fnc_parlament_" + c + "_rural_support"] > 0) {
            Q["fnc_parlament_" + c + "_rural_support"] += 1.5;
            Q["fnc_parlament_" + c + "_retired_support"] += 1;
        } else {
            Q["abstain_parlament_" + c + "_rural_support"] += 1.5;
            Q["fnc_parlament_" + c + "_retired_support"] += 1;
        }
        Q["cup_parlament_" + c + "_rural_support"] += 7;
        Q[_activeCiu + "_parlament_" + c + "_rural_support"] += 5.5;
        Q["erc_parlament_" + c + "_retired_support"] -= 10;
        Q[_activeCiu + "_parlament_" + c + "_retired_support"] += 5;
        Q["abstain_parlament_" + c + "_retired_support"] += 2;
        Q["cup_parlament_" + c + "_retired_support"] += 2;
        Q["erc_parlament_" + c + "_unemployed_support"] -= 5;
        Q["abstain_parlament_" + c + "_unemployed_support"] += 1.5;
        Q["cup_parlament_" + c + "_unemployed_support"] += 1.5;
        Q[_activeCiu + "_parlament_" + c + "_unemployed_support"] += 2;
    }

    if(Q.icv_parlament_s > 0) {
        Q.icv_relations += 10;
    } else if (Q.csqp_parlament_s > 0) {
        Q.csqp_relations += 10;
    } else if (Q.cecp_parlament_s > 0) {
        Q.cecp_relations += 10;
    } else {
        Q.ecp_relations += 10;
    }

    Q[_activeCiu + "_relations"] -= 15;
!}

This decision is highly disappointing not only for the leadership at [? if cdc_parlament_s > 0: CDC?][? if dl_parlament_s > 0: DL?][? if pdcat_parlament_s > 0: the PDeCAT?], but also within the party. Internal tensions are rising as some see it as throwing away the once-in-a-generation chance to actually push for a unified front for independence. 

- @post_event: Hope we took the right decision here...

@erc_jxsi_formation
on-arrival: {!
    if (!Q.achievement_jxsi) {
        window.achievementNotif('Junts pel Sí', 'img/parties/logo_jxsi.png', 1);
    }
    this.achieve("jxsi");

    Q.jxsi_roadmap = 2;
    Q.roadmap_year = Q.year + 2;
    Q.erc_in_jxsi = true;
    Q.player_in_jxsi = true;
    const _activeCiu = Q.cdc_parlament_s > 0 ? "cdc" : Q.dl_parlament_s > 0 ? "dl" : "pdcat";
    Q[_activeCiu + "_in_jxsi"] = true;

    Q.jxsi_parlament_s = Q[_activeCiu + "_parlament_s"] + Q.erc_parlament_s;
    Q.erc_parlament_s = 0;
    Q[_activeCiu + "_parlament_s"] = 0;

    // block parlament card from appearing
    Q.cat_caretaker_gov = true;
    if (Q.cat_coalition.includes(_activeCiu) || Q.cat_coalition.includes("erc")) {
        Q.position_disp = "<span style='font-style: italic'>Government Support</span>";
    } 

    for (const c of Q.parlament_constituencies) {
        Q["abstain_parlament_" + c + "_buss_support"] -= 1;
        Q["abstain_parlament_" + c + "_ind_support"] -= 1;
        Q["abstain_parlament_" + c + "_middle_support"] -= 2;
        Q["abstain_parlament_" + c + "_unemployed_support"] -= 1;
        Q["abstain_parlament_" + c + "_young_support"] -= 2;
        Q["abstain_parlament_" + c + "_retired_support"] -= 2;
        Q["abstain_parlament_" + c + "_rural_support"] -= 2.5;
        Q["jxsi_parlament_" + c + "_buss_support"] =  Q[_activeCiu + "_parlament_" + c + "_buss_support"] + Q["erc_parlament_" + c + "_buss_support"] + 0.5;
        Q["jxsi_parlament_" + c + "_ind_support"] += Q[_activeCiu + "_parlament_" + c + "_ind_support"] + Q["erc_parlament_" + c + "_ind_support"] - 1;
        Q["jxsi_parlament_" + c + "_middle_support"] += Q[_activeCiu + "_parlament_" + c + "_middle_support"] + Q["erc_parlament_" + c + "_middle_support"] - 1;
        Q["jxsi_parlament_" + c + "_unemployed_support"] += Q[_activeCiu + "_parlament_" + c + "_unemployed_support"] + Q["erc_parlament_" + c + "_unemployed_support"] - 3;
        Q["jxsi_parlament_" + c + "_young_support"] += Q[_activeCiu + "_parlament_" + c + "_young_support"] + Q["erc_parlament_" + c + "_young_support"] - 2;
        Q["jxsi_parlament_" + c + "_retired_support"] += Q[_activeCiu + "_parlament_" + c + "_retired_support"] + Q["erc_parlament_" + c + "_retired_support"] + 1.5;
        Q["jxsi_parlament_" + c + "_rural_support"] += Q[_activeCiu + "_parlament_" + c + "_rural_support"] + Q["erc_parlament_" + c + "_rural_support"] + 0.75;
        if (Q.jxsi_formation_num == 40) {
            // Anti-ciu, indy vote goes to CUP
            Q["cup_parlament_" + c + "_buss_support"] += 0.5;
            Q["cup_parlament_" + c + "_ind_support"] += 2;
            Q["cup_parlament_" + c + "_middle_support"] += 3;
            Q["cup_parlament_" + c + "_unemployed_support"] += 4;
            Q["cup_parlament_" + c + "_young_support"] += 4;
            Q["cup_parlament_" + c + "_retired_support"] += 0.5;
            Q["cup_parlament_" + c + "_rural_support"] += 1.75;
        } else {
            Q["jxsi_parlament_" + c + "_buss_support"] += 0.5;
            Q["jxsi_parlament_" + c + "_ind_support"] += 2;
            Q["jxsi_parlament_" + c + "_middle_support"] += 3;
            Q["jxsi_parlament_" + c + "_unemployed_support"] += 4;
            Q["jxsi_parlament_" + c + "_young_support"] += 4;
            Q["jxsi_parlament_" + c + "_retired_support"] += 0.5;
            Q["cup_parlament_" + c + "_rural_support"] += 1.75;
        }
        Q["erc_parlament_" + c + "_buss_support"] = 0;
        Q["erc_parlament_" + c + "_ind_support"] = 0;
        Q["erc_parlament_" + c + "_middle_support"] = 0;
        Q["erc_parlament_" + c + "_unemployed_support"] = 0;
        Q["erc_parlament_" + c + "_young_support"] = 0;
        Q["erc_parlament_" + c + "_retired_support"] = 0;
        Q["erc_parlament_" + c + "_rural_support"] = 0;
        Q[_activeCiu + "_parlament_" + c + "_buss_support"] = 0;
        Q[_activeCiu + "_parlament_" + c + "_ind_support"] = 0;
        Q[_activeCiu + "_parlament_" + c + "_middle_support"] = 0;
        Q[_activeCiu + "_parlament_" + c + "_unemployed_support"] = 0;
        Q[_activeCiu + "_parlament_" + c + "_young_support"] = 0;
        Q[_activeCiu + "_parlament_" + c + "_retired_support"] = 0;
        Q[_activeCiu + "_parlament_" + c + "_rural_support"] = 0;
    }

    Q.independence_movement += 5;
    Q.independence_trust += 15;
!}

The jxsi coalition has been formed! It now counts with ample support from civil society organizations, minor parties like SI, as well as, of course, the big players in the Parlament, [? if cdc_in_jxsi > 0: CDC?][? if dl_in_jxsi > 0: DL?][? if pdcat_in_jxsi > 0: the PDeCAT?] and ERC. Can it, however, be expanded further? Everyone is looking right now at the CUP, who so far has been skeptical of the whole formation process. Will they join in as well to build true National unity?

-@jxsi_cup_in
-@jxsi_cup_no

@jxsi_cup_in
title: Push the CUP to join in!
subtitle: Despite some heavy criticisms of the role of [? if cdc_in_jxsi > 0: CDC?][? if dl_in_jxsi > 0: DL?][? if pdcat_in_jxsi > 0: the PDeCAT?] within jxsi, it seems like they can be convinced after all with a bit of a push. [-1 resources]
choose-if: cup_relations >= 65 and jxsi_formation_num == 50 and party_resouces >= 1
unavailable-subtitle: [? if cup_relations >= 65: We don't have good enough relations with the CUP. ?][? if jxsi_formation_num != 40: There's no way they can accept a [? if cdc_in_jxsi > 0: CDC?][? if dl_in_jxsi > 0: DL?][? if pdcat_in_jxsi > 0: PDeCAT?] leadership. ?][? if party_resources < 1: Not enough resources.?]
on-arrival: {!
    // TODO: make a poble lliure leadership also a requisite?
    const _activeComuns = Q.icv_parlament_s > 0 ? "icv" : Q.csqp_parlament_s > 0 ? "csqp" : Q.cecp_parlament_s > 0 ? "cecp" : "ecp";
    Q.jxsi_parlament_s += Q.cup_parlament_s;
    Q.cup_parlament_s = 0;
    for (const c of Q.parlament_constituencies) {
        for (const d of Q.parlament_demographics) {
            Q["jxsi_parlament_" + c + "_" + d + "_support"] += Q["cup_parlament_" + c + "_" + d + "_support"] * 0.7;
            Q["abstain_parlament_" + c + "_" + d + "_support"] += Q["cup_parlament_" + c + "_" + d + "_support"] * 0.1;
            Q[_activeComuns + "_parlament_" + c + "_" + d + "_support"] += Q["cup_parlament_" + c + "_" + d + "_support"] * 0.2;
            Q["cup_parlament_" + c + "_" + d + "_support"] = 0;
        }
    }
    Q.independence_movement += 2;
    Q.independence_trust += 10;
    Q.cup_in_jxsi = true;
    Q.party_resources -= 1;
!}

@jxsi_cup_no
title: The CUP stays out of the coalition
subtitle: [? if jxsi_formation_num != 50: Something about betraying the original idea of a civic list and instead doing yet another party-centric coalition ?]

Seems like National unity will have to do without the CUP for now. Even without them, this is a huge step forward for the upcoming elections! The vote of our lives!

-@post_event: Let's hope we don't need them down the line though...

@cup_0
on-arrival: {!
    if (!Q.achievement_jxsi) {
