    Q[_activeCiu + "_in_jxsi"] = true;
    Q.cat_caretaker_gov = true;
!}

The biggest point of contention, of course, is leadership and party splitting of the coalition. Traditionally dominant [? if cdc_parlament_s > 0: CDC?][? if dl_parlament_s > 0: DL?][? if pdcat_parlament_s > 0: PDeCAT?] is pushing to maintain its dominance, but if they truly want to build National unity with us, we may be able to push for a less party-centred and more civil-lead proposal.

- @cup_irl
- @cup_romeva

@cup_irl
title: [? if cdc_parlament_s > 0: CDC's candidate, [+ cdc_leader +]?][? if dl_parlament_s > 0: DL's candidate, [+ dl_leader +]?][? if pdcat_parlament_s > 0: PDeCAT's candidate, [+ pdcat_leader +]?] takes the helm
