With [? if cdc_parlament_s > 0: [+ cdc_leader +]?][? if dl_parlament_s > 0: [+ dl_leader +]?][? if pdcat_parlament_s > 0: [+ pdcat_leader +]?] at the forefront of jxsi, the party has grown increasingly skeptical of the idea of joining in. Disguised as a National-unity Front for independence and self-determination, the candidacy seems to instead perpetuate the reign of austerity and alleged corruption of the Catalan bourgeois-right. Both ERC and [? if cdc_parlament_s > 0: CDC?][? if dl_parlament_s > 0: DL?][? if pdcat_parlament_s > 0: the PDeCAT?], nonetheless, are adamant that we join in.

- @cup_no_join
