Without the expected [? if cdc_parlament_s > 0: [+ cdc_leader +]?][? if dl_parlament_s > 0: [+ dl_leader +]?][? if pdcat_parlament_s > 0: [+ pdcat_leader +]?] leadership, the jxsi candidacy seems to have taken a slightly different meaning within the party. While there's still suspicion about it being a way to disguise the reign of austerity and alleged corruption of the Catalan bourgeois-right, with a stronger non-partisan leadership there's hope that the CUP and ERC can keep that at bay to an extent at least. Both ERC and [? if cdc_parlament_s > 0: CDC?][? if dl_parlament_s > 0: DL?][? if pdcat_parlament_s > 0: the PDeCAT?], in any case, are adamant that we join in.

